Testing the APIs
Use tools like Postman or cURL to test the endpoints.

Initialize DB: GET http://localhost:3000/api/initialize
List Transactions: GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?search=...&page=1&perPage=10
Statistics: GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics?month=January
Bar Chart Data: GET http://localhost:3000/api/barchart?month=January
Pie Chart Data: GET http://localhost:3000/api/piechart?month=January
Combined Response: GET http://localhost:3000/api/combined?month=January